  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A jet-black snuff ground from the resin of coalshade trees. A pinch sharpens the senses and steadies the hands; the price is a bone-deep restlessness that lingers for hours.</p><p><strong><em>Desired effects on use.</em></strong> For one hour you have a +2 bonus to Wisdom (Perception) and Dexterity (Sleight of Hand) checks, and you have advantage on initiative rolls.</p><p><strong><em>On use, save against addiction.</em></strong> Make a DC 13 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, you gain the Addicted condition from Coalshade Powder (see below).</p><p><strong><em>Addicted from Coalshade Powder.</em></strong> While you have this Addicted condition, you are also Poisoned and have disadvantage on Wisdom checks.</p><p><strong><em>Withdrawal Modifier: 4.</em></strong> Withdrawal lasts max(4 − your Constitution modifier, 2) long rests, minimum 1.</p><p><em>Requires: Snuff Horn.</em></p>"
    },
